Students clutch resumes inside branded folders and compare swag items such as water bottles and phone chargers. An announcement chimes, signaling the final hour of the fair. Meanwhile, a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, and career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact. A whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths.

Additionally, a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, while alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station. Tech companies display demo screens showing their latest apps, and representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom. Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance.
